ZooKeeper Server Start: 
bin/zookeeper-server-start.sh config/zookeeper.properties

Kafka Server Start: 
bin/kafka-server-start.sh config/kafka.properties

Create Topic: 
bin/kafka-topics.sh --create --topic topicName --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

List Topics on a Server:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --list --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

Describe Topic:
bin/kafka-topics.sh --describe --topic topicName --bootstrap-server localhost:9092

Producer Write Into Topic:
bin/kafka-console-producer.sh --topic topicName --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
> This is the message.
> You can keep writing here.
> If you want to exit, press ctrl + c.

Consumer Reading Topic:
bin/kafka-console-consumer.sh --topic topicName --from-beginning --bootstrap-server localhost:9092
This is the message.
You can keep writing here.
If you want to exit, press ctrl + c.


